<br>
Oh Contraire!<br>
<br>
Speaking of a sploit is much much different than speaking of a spoiler.<br>
<br>
A sploit is spoken of because deep down we would rather they fixe the sploit so the game is more challenging as designed.<br>
<br>
A spoiler is describing content that is designed to be experianced rather than be spoon fed via other's experiance.<br>
<br>
Take for example a Guide grabbing your raidleader by the hand and walking your raid through content to get to the endgame vs. DOING the content on your own and feeling the sense of accomplishment via your success.<br>
<br>
The former (sploit) is acceptable, the latter (Spoiler), on TCH is not.  They are Quite different in nature actually ergo the leper comment is true of Spoilers.<br>
<br>
Laerwyn <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=934151">Toys</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://p201.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tamsindyresoul>Tamsin Dyresoul</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_magentaspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Minstrel</span><br>  Posts: 184<br> <font color=#330000>(6/21/04 8:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19525.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~</span><hr size=1> Bah, way to give a spoiler on the sploit vs spoiler argument.  Laerwyn is now a leper to us all! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
